name: December Tote
description:
This lovely tote bag is perfect for taking to the beach and strolling the shops this summer. It is handmade in Melbourne using canvas and a little bit of leather. It has french seams and the front has been hand printed using a potato stamp.

This tote is available in charcoal and cream and measures, 32.5 cm wide by 39.5cm length. The strap length is 62cm

name: Esme Bum Bag (Aqua Grey and Black)
description:
Was £85 now only £59!

This multi functional bag comes in two colours and can either be worn as a shoulder bag or looped through a belt to become a bum bag. Perfect for music festivals, traveling and anywhere else where you want your arms free.

The strap is adjustable and detachable with strong clasps and the two leather loops on the back are perfect for threading a belt through. 

The internal of this bag has one small pocket and 4 card holder pockets.

Measurements:
Width: 13cm
Depth: 3cm at the top, narrowing to 1.5cm at bottom
Loops: 5cm long 
Strap: 132cm (adjustable longer and shorter)

name: Seaside Collection Wallets
description: These wallets have all been handmade in Melbourne. They are made out of assorted fabrics and have one zip pocket, 8 card holders (can fit more than one card per slot), and two notes areas.

name: Sadie Satchel (Black or Brown)
description:
Was $170 now only $119

This leather satchel is designed to fit most things including journals and small laptops. It can be worn on one shoulder or across the body and has a hand printed and designed lining. 

This large satchel features two external front pockets with magnetic clasps, two internal pockets, one internal zip pocket, two internal pen holder pockets and one external zip pocket on the back of the bag. It also has an adjustable strap. 

Measurements:
Width: 34cm
Height: 32cm
Depth: 6.5cm
Strap length: 76cm (adjustable to be bigger and smaller)

Available in two colours, Black or dark Brown
